Package: stmCorrViz
Type: Package
Title: A Tool for Structural Topic Model Visualizations
Version: 1.1
Date: 2015-02-14
Imports: jsonlite, stm
Authors@R: c(person("Antonio", "Coppola", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "acoppola@college.harvard.edu"),
	      person("Brandon", "Stewart", role = c("aut", "cph")),
	      person("Margaret", "Roberts", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
	      person("Dustin", "Tingley", role = c("ctb", "ths", "cph")))
Author: Antonio Coppola [aut, cre, cph], Brandon Stewart [aut, cph], Margaret Roberts [ctb, cph], Dustin Tingley [ctb, ths, cph]
Maintainer: Antonio Coppola <acoppola@college.harvard.edu>
Description: A tool for hierarchical visualizations of the Structural Topic Model (STM) of Roberts, Stewart, and Tingley. The package allows the user to generate interactive visualizations highlighting correlations among topics, and can be used to view the model at differing levels of complexity.
License: GPL (>= 2)
